snippet.title: Diatomic - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Diatomic!
Available June 25th!

Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2864680/Diatomic/
Website - diatomicstudios.com

Diatomic is Complete with over 30+ Levels of face paced action, gun juggling, epic boss fights, hardcore parkour and more blood and chaos than the term "fantasy violence" should probably allow for!

Kill - Steal weapon - kill again!

Health and weaponry can all be gained from killing enemies as you charge through this arena shooter by sprinting, parkouring off walls or by flying through the air with your grappling hook!

Key Features

[list]
-   Fast Paced Action
-   Gun Juggling 
-   Parkour
-   Grapple Swinging
-   30+ Levels
-   70+ Weapons
-   20+ Enemy Types
-   Boss Fights!
-   Agility challenges
-   Destructible Environments

Song = STRLGHT - ALL GAS NO BREAKS
